title: Rockwood - Remodeled 2 Bed, 1 Bath w/Stainless Steel Appliances!
posting_body: ["Are you looking for an apartment that isn't just cozy but is also modern and on-trend with current interior designs?", 'If so then this is the apartment for you!', 'This 2-bedroom, 1-bathroom unit features new appliances including a refrigerator, stove, dishwasher, and microwave.', 'This unit also boasts beautiful, modern subway tiling, new paint, and new fixtures throughout.', 'The building is in Rockwood.', 'Sorry, No Pets.', 'Unit features:', '-New Stainless-Steel Appliances (Refrigerator, Microwave, Stove, and Dishwasher.)', '-New Kitchen Cabinets', '-Beautiful Modern Subway Tiling', '-Gorgeous White Cabinetry', '-Beautiful Granite Countertops', '$945 Rent / $945 Security Deposit', 'Available Now!', 'For more information or to schedule an appointment for showing call', 'show contact info', 'Also enjoy features such as online rent payment, online maintenance requests, and online applications.', 'Thank you for your interest.', 'Cities close by Southgate, Wyandotte, Riverview, Trenton, Gibraltar, Woodhaven, and Brownstown.']
